{"tid":1530940,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"尋國泰貨運HR妹妹","createTime":"2019-09-02T05:48:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T04:32:23.000Z","uid":266069,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"520019eb63105c12204f57fc8fcedabf45e7d423","tid":1530940,"uid":266069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:48:05.000Z","msg":"前排八月頭報左<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">國泰空運服務主任</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Interview 個陣有個應該係九十後既HR妹妹幫我對資料 好好笑容又幾靚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">重點係有啲異國風情既感覺 少少ABC/混血feel</span></strong></span> 我唔記得帶cert佢又笑笑口好nice咁話可以後補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個陣已經幾留意佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後有offer上黎簽約都係佢幫我手 諗住睇佢staff card又睇唔清楚又唔敢問佢咩名 咁唯有等遲啲上人事部或者係canteen巧遇下佢啦, 點知成個幾禮拜都冇再見過佢.....有冇人知佢係咪被辭職？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又有冇人知佢咩名 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: large;\">眼大大， 中長頭髮偏啡， 上次見佢係著白色恤衫</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我見人事部都唔算多人應該幾易認 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望可以識下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d9a124534a363a6d563c7a6881d1d66a7e5ba71","tid":1530940,"uid":266069,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:49:15.000Z","msg":"自推十連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/no